parameters.name: eflux1
parameters.description:
Electron flux from the first energy bin    
                          listed in the E_BINS.TAB file for these data.

                          missing_constant = 9.999E-99 represents the flagged values from the instrument team.
                          error_constant = -9.99E-99 represents the flagged value from the PPI Node.

parameters.name: eflux2
parameters.description:
Electron flux from the second energy bin    
                          listed in the E_BINS.TAB file for these data.

                          missing_constant = 9.999E-99 represents the flagged values from the instrument team.
                          error_constant = -9.99E-99 represents the flagged value from the PPI Node.
